---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();

const eventLinks = [
	{ label: '돌잔치', href: '/events/doljanchi' },
	{ label: '칠·팔순', href: '/events/hwangab' },
	{ label: '스몰웨딩', href: '/events/wedding' },
	{ label: '세미나', href: '/events/seminar' },
	{ label: '피자체험', href: '/events/pizza-class' },
	{ label: '졸업식', href: '/events/graduation' },
];
---

<footer class="border-t border-border-warm mt-32 bg-bg">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-10 text-sm">
		<!-- 브랜드 -->
		<div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
			<a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 group w-fit">
				<img 
					src="/images/logo.svg" 
					alt="The Old Mill" 
					class="h-8 w-auto transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
				/>
				<span class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide">THE OLD MILL</span>
			</a>
			<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
				충남 아산의 가족 레스토랑.<br />
				소중한 순간을 함께하는 공간입니다.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- 행사 안내 -->
		<div>
			<div class="font-medium mb-4 text-ink">행사 안내</div>
			<ul class="text-muted space-y-2.5">
				{eventLinks.map(link => (
					<li>
						<a href={link.href} class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">
							{link.label}
						</a>
					</li>
				))}
			</ul>
		</div>

		<!-- 방문 안내 -->
		<div>
			<div class="font-medium mb-4 text-ink">방문 안내</div>
			<ul class="text-muted space-y-2.5">
				<li>매일 11:00 - 21:30</li>
				<li>라스트오더<br/>점심 15:00 / 저녁 20:30</li>
				<li class="pt-2">
					<a href="/space" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">
						공간 둘러보기 →
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<!-- 예약 및 문의 -->
		<div>
			<div class="font-medium mb-4 text-ink">예약 및 문의</div>
			<ul class="text-muted space-y-2.5">
				<li>
					<a href="tel:041-546-1080" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">
						041-546-1080
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>충남 아산시 (상세 주소)</li>
				<li class="pt-2">
					<a href="/contact" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">
						문의 페이지 →
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="border-t border-border-warm">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 text-xs text-muted flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-3">
			<div>© {currentYear} The Old Mill. All rights reserved.</div>
			<div class="flex gap-5">
				<a href="/about" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">소개</a>
				<a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">개인정보처리방침</a>
				<a href="/terms" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">이용약관</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>